description:
Blondie is looking for a win any way she can get one, She has lost every match and was eliminated in the first round of the Summer Vengeance tournament. She was eliminated by "The Rogue", and now we have a grudge match.
The last time the Rogue was on the mat she left it in an ambulance. This is her first match back since a dislocated shoulder she suffered wrestling "The Goddess".
The season first re-match is match between last years ranked 11th and 12th. Blondie wants revenge, The Rogue wants to prove she is healthy, and ready to rock.
title: Amber Rayne "Rogue" (0-2) vs Sarah Ceylon "Blondie" (0-4)
